要聘用能对患者提供生活照护服务的医疗护理员，同时要加强陪护探视管理，可根据患者实际情况限定陪护人员数量，限定探视时间与人数，提倡采用电话、视频等方式进行探视”。 已有三甲医院开始试点 记者走进已开展“免陪护”试点的上海交通大学医学院附属仁济医院，该院已有两个病区实现住院患者由专业团队24小时全程照护。 资料来源上海三级医院全部试点：不要家属陪，专业护理员24小时全程照护_患者_病房_服务"},"attached_info":"CkIIjqfRqpW24I09EAMaCTExMzgzNTczNSC0q6m+BjAAOLIBQBZyCzE0Mjk4NDAwNTIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"107 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-32dda31792cd7cdca83678a7722921f0_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1741778311.442393","card_id":"Q_13289247152","target":{"id":13289247152,"title":"猫咪为啥会陪人睡一晚上呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/13289247152","type":"question","created":1740445479,"answer_count":27,"follower_count":42,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[954,1570,1571,56928],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我家小blue会在我睡着后 陪我睡一晚上 睡很久很久"},"attached_info":"CkEIjqfRqpW24I09EAMaCTExMzYzMzE0OSCnrvS9BjAAOCpAF3ILMTMyODkyNDcxNTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"107 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c6f8a5c9e05a682913c7738c6826dac9_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1741778311.442840","card_id":"Q_14703809988","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":14703809988,"title":"独生子女三十而立开始给爸妈养老，「421」家庭结构下养老有哪些问题？怎样能更好照顾父母？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14703809988","type":"question","created":1741697038,"answer_count":20,"follower_count":49,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5376,13095,16950,1